title: 45: Moments faking it till you make it
itunes:title: Moments faking it till you make it
description: Sometimes we’re under the wave longer than we’d like to be, I definitely have been. For a few weeks now I’ve been struggling to remember what it feels like to enjoy all of the beauty in life’s little moments. We’re healing together & I want to talk about it some more. The key is shifting the mindset & faking it till you make it - and soon you feel healed and grateful.
itunes:author: Lexi Hidalgo
dc:creator: Lexi Hidalgo
